ww.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-sandwich-counter-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-sandwich-counter-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>两名<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/starfield"><em>Starfield</em></a>粉丝正在倒计时，直到<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/bethesda-softworks">Bethesda</a>最新的角色扮演游戏推出，该游戏带有一个可以在三明治中计时的计时器。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/starfield-fan-calculates-spaceships-will-cost-about-64-cheese-sandwiches-3470456">《Starfield》发行日期、最新消息和我们所知道的一切</a></strong></li></ul><p>Twitch 主播 Blurbs 和 3D 建模师兼艺术家 Anik Deysigns 合作创建了<a href="https://starfieldsandwich.com/">starfieldsandwich.com</a> ，该网站将观众带到一艘正在眺望太空的船上的房间。每隔五分钟，就会从天花板上分发出一个三明治，倒计时结束后，三明治可能会填满地板。</p><blockquote class="reddit-embed-bq" style="height:240px" ><p> <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/Starfield/comments/15y9u2o/its_time_i_made_you_all_a_countdown_website_that/">是时候了！我为大家制作了一个倒计时网站，该网站将每 5 分钟发布一次三明治，一直到启动！</a><br />由<a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/Blurbss">u/Blurbss</a>在<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/Starfield/">Starfield</a>提供</p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://embed.reddit.com/widgets.js" charset="UTF-8"></script></p><p>从倒计时开始到 9 月 1 日<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/pc">PC</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X|S 版</a><em>《Starfield</em> 》抢先体验启动期间，房间内将有超过 2,500 个三明治。但这不仅仅是一个循环动画。</p><p> “距离抢先体验还有不到十天的时间，我想为社区提供一些很酷的东西来帮助打发时间，”Blurbs 说。 “随着堆的增加，一定要每天检查，更不用说随着我们接近发布，某些‘事情’可能会开始发生。”</p><p>其中一个事件是出现在黑暗太空中的虫洞，它开始从<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-elder-scrolls-v-skyrim"><em>天际</em></a>散发出甜面包卷、奶酪轮等。</p><p> “虽然极其愚蠢，但这实际上需要多人投入大量的工作。我们真诚地希望您喜欢它并随时分享！”流光继续。</p><p>对<em>《Starfield</em> 》三明治的关注源于这样一种认识：与当代标准相比，游戏中食品的估价似乎出奇地高。 </p><figure id="attachment_3479453" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3479453" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3479453" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-leaked-pre-load-listing-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-leaked-pre-load-listing-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-leaked-pre-load-listing-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-leaked-pre-load-listing-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-leaked-pre-load-listing-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-leaked-pre-load-listing-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-leaked-pre-load-listing-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3479453" class="wp-caption-text"> “星空”信用：贝塞斯达</figcaption></figure><p>于是， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/starfield-fan-calculates-spaceships-will-cost-about-64-cheese-sandwiches-3470456">玩家计算出，一整艘飞船的价值相当于65个三明治</a>。</p><p>此外，制作人杰米·马洛里透露了她在海盗星域游戏中的秘密乐趣—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/starfield-dev-becomes-a-hero-for-being-a-sandwich-stealing-pirate-3477656">从敌船上偷走所有三明治并将它们存放在自己的货舱中</a>。她还有一艘三明治形状的宇宙飞船，她将其命名为“烧烤者”。</p><p>马洛里说：“这个名字本身就令人恐惧，但当你在过场动画中亲眼目睹这个巨大的潜艇般的创造物优雅地降落或在宇宙中飞驰时，它就是纯粹的喜剧黄金。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/starfield-fans-create-sandwich-countdown-in-space-while-waiting-for-launch-3487494">《Starfield》粉丝在等待发射时在太空中制作三明治倒计时的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 PlayStation Portal，也称为 Project Q，比 Steam Deck 更轻https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/playstation-portal-also-known-as-project-q-is-lighter-than-the-steam-deck-3487464?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign= Playstation 门户也称为 Project Q 比 Steam 平台更轻Imogen DonovanWed, 23 Aug 2023 15:12:09 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPlayStation 5 https://www.nme.com/?p=3487464 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/ps-portable-200-dollars.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/ps-portable-200-dollars.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/ps-portable-200-dollars-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/ps-portable-200-dollars-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/ps-portable-200-dollars-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/ps-portable-200-dollars-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/ps-portable-200-dollars-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>它不支持 PlayStation Plus Premium 游戏的串流</p><p>后<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/playstation-portal-also-known-as-project-q-is-lighter-than-the-steam-deck-3487464">PlayStation Portal（也称为 Project Q）比</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上的 Steam Deck 更轻。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/ps-portable-200-dollars.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/ps-portable-200-dollars.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/ps-portable-200-dollars-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/ps-portable-200-dollars-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/ps-portable-200-dollars-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/ps-portable-200-dollars-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/ps-portable-200-dollars-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> PlayStation Portal 是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/sony-project-q-handheld-ps5-streaming-device-3447901">Project Q</a>的新名称，这款手持设备让玩家有机会在家中以 1080p 分辨率、60fps 传输<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ps5">PS5</a>游戏。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/psvr2-review-3403470">PSVR2 评论：VRy 令人兴奋</a></strong></li></ul><p>这一新信息来自索尼和<em><a href="https://www.ign.com/articles/playstation-portal-hands-on-with-sonys-new-remote-play-handheld" target="_blank" rel="noopener">IGN</a></em>的 Bo Moore 的一篇<a href="https://blog.playstation.com/2023/08/23/playstations-first-remote-play-dedicated-device-playstation-portal-remote-player-to-launch-later-this-year-at-199-99/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">博文</a>，他在今天（8 月 23 日）早些时候分享了他对 PlayStation Portal 的亲身体验。 PlayStation Portal 与 PlayStation Portable 仅一字之差，但最现代版本的设计无疑是“爱它或恨它”的一个例子。</p><p>它是一个 8 英寸 LCD 屏幕，位于伸出的 DualSense 控制器的中间，根据摩尔的结论，这并不是描述该设备的不准确方式。自适应触发器、触摸板和触觉反馈都包含在 PlayStation Portal 中，尽管触摸板被放置在屏幕左下角和右下角的两个单独的点上。</p><p> PlayStation Portal 旨在“消除标准流媒体和手持体验的痛点”。 Moore 指出，该设备比<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/nintendo-switch">Nintendo Switch</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/steam-deck">Steam Deck</a>更轻，但不会影响视觉效果或控制的舒适度。 </p><figure id="attachment_3487491" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3487491" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3487491" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/ps-portable-200-dollars-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/ps-portable-200-dollars-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/ps-portable-200-dollars-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-cont